org.jtimer.Annotations

Annotation Type Time


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Time
    Used to specifiy that this method should be timed. repeat() Has a repeat option, be default this is 10. This is the number of times that the test will be repeated. timeout() Has a timeout time, be default there is no timeout. The timeout is in nanosecond and a test will be be halted after the timeout has been reached.
    Author:
    MagneticZero
